  <p>The table below demonstrates the invariance property of the odds ratio for Investigation 3.9. Notice that the odds ratio remains constant at 9.385 regardless of how we set up the comparison, while the relative risk changes depending on the setup.</p>

  <tabular halign="center" top="minor" bottom="minor" left="minor" right="minor">
    <col halign="left"/>
    <row header="yes">
      <cell></cell>
      <cell>Odds Ratio</cell>
      <cell>Relative Risk</cell>
    </row>
    <row>
      <cell>Of lung cancer comparing smokers to non-smokers</cell>
      <cell><m>\frac{583/576}{22/204} = 9.385</m></cell>
